experience.description:
1. Achievement of targets for quota;
2. Building the work of the sales department;
3. Management of the sales department;
4. Development and implementation of BP;
5. Implementation of CRM based on Bitrix24;
6. Project management.

Main responsibilities:
- operational management of the retail chain of grocery stores (9 stores);
- setting tasks and monitoring their implementation (subordinate to up to 100 people);
- ensuring break-even network activity, sales management;
- development and implementation of a network development strategy, budget management, analysis and control of operating expenses;
- ensuring the financial efficiency of stores (sales plan, percentage of service, average bill);
- achievement of profitability indicators (cost optimization, reduction of production costs);
- Administrative management of retail outlets (location definitions, lease relations, organization of the supply and storage process).

Results of work and achievements:
- exceeded the revenue figure of 300 million rubles;
- Revenues exceeded 27 thousand from 1m2;
- IRR not worse than 24%
- developed and implemented key business processes in the retail network;
- launched the work of outlets 8 stores;
- formed an effective team;
- implemented a checklist system for line personnel management (KPI);
- implemented a project to automate retail operations with subsequent accounting (based on 1C).

Projects and consulting activities
Russia
Project manager, CEO, external manager (anti-crisis manager), financial director
In the period 2000-2011. took part in the implementation of various projects as CEO, managing partner, financial director, advisor.

Examples of completed projects:
1. GK "Lido" (Ufa, 2010-2011) - external manager (CEO) group of companies.
Tasks:
- development and implementation of a program to improve business efficiency;
- management of structural changes in a group of companies (about 1000 employees).
Results:
- ensured a 20% reduction in the group's costs;
- increased the speed of revolutions by 2.5 times;
- provided a monthly income in cash;
- increased profitability (+ 10%), marginality (+ 20%);
- built a management structure for organizations "from scratch", introduced new management tools (integrated monitoring unit);
- trained and prepared employees to fill 4 TOP managers in the company.
2. GC "House of Finance" (Moscow, 2009-2010) Managing partner, financial director.
Tasks:
- sales of consulting services for the organization of external financing for industrial enterprises;
- creation of project teams;
- personal sales and project management.
Results:
- ensured the execution of 3 transactions:
1. redemption of industrial assets;
2. organization of financing for Sberbank;
3. management of the client's credit portfolio
4. receiving subsidies for small and medium-sized businesses

3.  Automobile plant “Altai” (Biysk, 2008-2009) CEO
Tasks:
- operational business management;
- business retention in a falling market;
- implementation of a new sales model.
Results:
- implemented anti-crisis management: ensured repayment of accounts payable in full, avoided bankruptcy procedures;
- the credit rating of an international organization for the owner of the company has been preserved;
- ensured the absence of claims and lawsuits, penalties for products sold;
- showed the economy of the planned budget.

4. ITERA LLC (Moscow, 2005-2007) Advisor to the General Director
Tasks:
- evaluation of investment projects;
- participation in the development of the investment program of the group;
- project management.
Results:
- implemented a project to create an oil terminal (asset "ITERA-SAMARA", Samara).

5. "Korund" (Dzerzhinsk, 2004-2005) head of the corporate department.
Tasks:
- search and purchase of specialized chemical industries;
- integration of acquired companies into a group of companies;
- implementation and maintenance of corporate standards and procedures.
Results:
- 6 business acquisition transactions were completed.

6. "RIN" (Moscow, 2000-2004) Financial Director
Tasks:
- Leading project teams;
- control over compliance with the budgets of operational groups and the entire company;
- ensuring the level of proper financing of the company's activities.
Results:
- more than 40 industrial enterprises were acquired;
- implementation of controlled bankruptcy procedures and completion of bankruptcy procedures with the planned result.

7. "Sputnik style" (Moscow, 2002 - 2017) Advisor for Finance and Development
Tasks:
- implementation of three key projects.
Results:
- realized the acquisition of assets for the company on a long-term installment plan using bill schemes;
- developed and implemented a tax scheme for the retail network (design and implementation);
- implementation of the accounting system 1C UPP and its adaptation with internal programs.

Property Protection Project Manager
Main responsibilities:
- development and implementation of programs to protect property from raider attacks and unfriendly influence;
- participation in bankruptcy proceedings in order to acquire industrial assets;
- project management;
- activities of an insolvency administrator by judicial appointment;

Results of work and achievements:
- successfully completed transactions for the acquisition of assets below market prices with participation in bankruptcy proceedings.
